txt.en: In the aftermath of the War of the Ring, the peoples of Anfalas and Pinnath Gelin mourn the loss of their Lords while struggling against the Corsairs of Umbar and other foes to restore a long-absent peace in Outer Gondor.
You have completed many quests in Outer Gondor and aided its people in the aftermath of the War of the Ring.
You have defeated many foes and made safe the lands of Outer Gondor.
You have thoroughly explored the lands of Anfalas and Pinnath Gelin in Outer Gondor.

In the aftermath of the War of the Ring, the peoples of Anfalas and Pinnath Gelin mourn the loss of their Lords while struggling against the Corsairs of Umbar and other foes to restore a long-absent peace in Outer Gondor.
